      "author": "Elisabet I",
      "authorUrl": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112381061513268870038?hl=id",
      "rating": 5,
      "text": "Dropping by for morning coffee or quick drink in between travel. Since it's available in the morning and located along the way when entering Bandung Pasteur, it's very helpful when in desperate need to get some drinks before going ahead with business trip.\n\nMaybe not the best place to sit down due to limited space available but at least there are some benches & tables available outside.",
      "textTranslated": "Mampir untuk minum kopi pagi atau minuman cepat di sela-sela perjalanan. Karena tersedia di pagi hari dan terletak di sepanjang jalan menuju Bandara Bandung Pasteur, tempat ini sangat membantu ketika sangat membutuhkan minuman sebelum melanjutkan perjalanan bisnis.\n\nMungkin bukan tempat terbaik untuk duduk karena ruang yang tersedia terbatas, tetapi setidaknya ada beberapa bangku & meja yang tersedia di luar.",
      "date": "2026-03-13T00:57:44.088Z",
